research/history/round_summaries/round_0075.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_e \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d e(x) \u662f\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5355\u4e2a expert\uff0c{B_e} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201crouter \u9009\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93 + \u5b50\u5e93\u5185 local top-k + \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5148\u7b5b\u6e05\u695a\uff1a`expert_topk` \u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_residual`\u3001`two_stage_residual_expert`\u3001`factorized_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8 frontier\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r74 \u4ec5\u628a `NUM_EXPERTS` \u4ece 128 \u63d0\u5230 256\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk`\u3001`K=160`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u548c\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\u65f6\uff0c\u7ee7\u7eed\u56de\u7b54 routed-only MoE-like \u524d\u6cbf\u7684\u6838\u5fc3\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5982\u679c r73\u2192r74 \u7684\u8fde\u7eed\u6539\u5584\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u7684\u4e3b\u8981\u74f6\u9888\u4ecd\u6709\u4e00\u90e8\u5206\u6765\u81ea\u603b\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\u5bb9\u91cf\u4e0d\u8db3\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f router \u8d28\u91cf\u6216 K \u9884\u7b97\u5df2\u7ecf\u9971\u548c\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48\u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u6269\u5927\u603b\u5bb9\u91cf\u3001\u540c\u65f6\u4fdd\u6301 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` \u7684\u77ed\u6fc0\u6d3b\u8def\u5f84\uff0c\u5e94\u80fd\u5728\u4ecd\u5904\u4e8e <0.5x \u7684\u8fd1\u540c\u4e00 total_cost \u4e0b\u7ee7\u7eed\u538b\u4f4e FVU\uff0c\u5e76\u66f4\u6e05\u695a\u5730\u754c\u5b9a\u8fd9\u6761\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u524d\u6cbf\u7684\u5bb9\u91cf\u6536\u76ca\u4f55\u65f6\u5f00\u59cb\u9971\u548c\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0075.json:38:      "\u5982\u679c\u8fd9\u4e00\u6b65\u4ecd\u6539\u5584\uff0c\u5219\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9 routed-only \u524d\u6cbf\u5c06\u5f97\u5230\u66f4\u5b8c\u6574\u7684\u5bb9\u91cf\u66f2\u7ebf\uff1b\u5982\u679c\u6539\u5584\u505c\u6b62\uff0c\u53ef\u66f4\u6709\u628a\u63e1\u5730\u628a\u540e\u7eed\u7ed3\u6784\u9884\u7b97\u8f6c\u5411 `lowrank_expert_residual` \u6216 `factorized_expert_topk` \u7b49\u65b9\u5411\u3002"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0075.json:42:      "\u5982\u679c `NUM_EXPERTS=256` \u6539\u5584\u6781\u5c0f\u6216\u505c\u6b62\uff0c\u5219\u53ef\u8f83\u6e05\u6670\u5224\u5b9a\u5f53\u524d `expert_topk` \u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u74f6\u9888\u5df2\u4e0d\u4e3b\u8981\u5728\u603b\u5b50\u5e93\u5bb9\u91cf\uff0c\u540e\u7eed\u5e94\u628a\u7ed3\u6784\u9884\u7b97\u8f6c\u56de `lowrank_expert_residual`\u3001`lowrank_expert_topk` \u6216 `factorized_expert_topk` \u8fd9\u7c7b\u5e26 shared basis / trunk / residual cleanup \u7684\u517c\u5bb9\u7ed3\u6784\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0087.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e(z)}(z)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 z = Bx 是共享低维投影，e(z) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{B_e} 对应若干静态 expert 子库，最终重构仍是静态向量库上的有限加权和。在线导出链路可写成“shared low-rank projection -> router 选静态 expert 子库 -> expert 内 low-rank head 做 local scoring/top-k -> 查表加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `factorized_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r74 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_topk` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，在保持 `K=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，shared-basis expert routing 能在仍处于低到中成本带的前提下，比 routed-only `expert_topk` 更有效地利用子库容量，从而把当前低开销 Pareto 前沿向下推进。按当前成本模型粗估，selection 约 0.33x、deployment 约 0.16x、total 约 0.49x，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","summary":"Round 87 不回到旧 family 的 K 轴微调，而是用一个高信息量、已实现但当前 target 尚未充分验证的结构方向补低成本前沿：以 r74 为 matched reference，只切换到 `factorized_expert_topk`。这直接回答提示里优先级很高的“expert 内 low-rank / shared-basis routing”是否比 routed-only MoE-like 更值得继续。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r74 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这不是 plain selector 的重复扫点，也不是当前主线 family 的 K 邻域打磨，而是对高优先级未充分验证结构 `shared low-rank basis + expert-specific head` 的 matched probe。主要风险是 auto `factorized_hidden_dim` 可能让 selection cost 接近 0.5x 带上沿，且该 family 若训练不稳定，首次结果可能更多体现优化难度而非结构上限；因此保留 sanity 更稳妥。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_expert_topk"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`factorized_expert_topk` 的最终导出形式仍是静态 expert 子库上的有限加权和；共享低秩投影与 expert head 只改变在线打分链路，不引入动态字典。","这轮是对提示里高优先级方向“expert 内 low-rank / shared-basis expert routing”的直接 matched 验证，比继续细扫 `expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的旧轴信息增量更高。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 粗估，`factorized_expert_topk K=160 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=128` 的 total_cost 约 0.49x，正好落在当前最需要补强的低成本带。","如果 sanity 或训练异常，先把问题归因为该 family 的实现/稳定性，而不是把单次失败上升成对 shared-basis expert routing 方向的结构性否定。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 在近同成本下明显优于 r74，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=128`，测试这条 shared-basis routed 前沿能否继续向左延伸。","如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 优于 r74 但仍明显落后于 <0.5x 最优点，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS` 或 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，区分瓶颈是在总静态容量还是 shared basis 宽度。","如果结果不如 r74，则说明当前 target 上 shared-basis scorer 还不足以单独形成新前沿，后续更应把预算转向 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert` 这类带 residual cleanup 的结构。"],"reference_round":74}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0095.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":94,"family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"40"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(·) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。在线侧仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单个静态 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容；`expert_topk` 属于直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 属于不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：r94 已证明把 `TRUNK_RANK` 从 64 压到 48 后，`lowrank + expert` 仍能在更低 total_cost 带形成新的可行点，说明 shared trunk 仍有压缩空间。相对 r94 仅将 `TRUNK_RANK: 48 -> 40`，若当前 Pareto knee 还未到达，则 FVU 应只小幅高于 0.1151，且能把这条兼容前沿继续左移到更低成本带，从而回答 `lowrank + expert` 的最小可用 shared trunk 是否已接近 40。","summary":"r94 刚在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上补出新的更低成本前沿点，因此本轮不切 family，也不回到 routed-only active-path 或 `factorized_expert_topk` 这些已给出负信号的方向。以 r94 为 reference，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=40`，继续精化这条 `lowrank + expert` 低成本线的 shared-trunk knee，优先争取新的更靠左非支配点。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r94 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。这不是旧 family 的 K 轴细扫，而是对刚刚取得正信号的兼容结构线做最小且高信息量的延伸。选择 40 而不是更激进的 32，是因为 r70 已表明 32 明显过薄；当前更合理的问题是 knee 是否位于 40-48 区间。主要风险是 40 仍会明显劣化，导致这轮只能得出“48 已接近最小可用 trunk”的结论；但这同样有价值，因为它能收敛后续低成本预算。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r94 (`lowrank_expert_topk TRUNK_RANK=48`) 以更低成本换到 FVU=0.1151，说明这条 `lowrank + expert` 线的 shared trunk 压缩并未在 48 处失效。","r93 (`expert_topk ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`) 仍是明确负信号，因此后续低成本预算不应继续投向 routed-only multi-expert active-path 扩展。","`factorized_expert_topk` 在 r90-r92 上稳定偏弱，当前优先级继续低于 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 trunk-knee 精化。","本轮若 `TRUNK_RANK=40` 仍能保住大部分质量，则说明当前 target 上 `lowrank + expert` 的可用 trunk 宽度还可继续低于 48。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `TRUNK_RANK=40` 继续形成非支配点，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=36`，完成这条低成本 knee 的更细分辨率搜索。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=40` 明显劣于 r94，则可初步判定这条 family 的最小可用 trunk 更接近 48；下一轮应停止继续压该轴，转去做 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert` 对照。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=40` 与 r94 基本持平但成本改善有限，则说明该 family 对 trunk 宽度已进入平台区，后续应减少局部压缩预算，转向更高信息量的结构切换。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0077.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e(h(x))}(h(x))} α_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低维投影，e(h(x)) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{b_{e,i}} 是各 expert 的静态子库原子。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“共享投影 -> router 选单个静态 expert 子库 -> expert 内 local top-k -> 静态库查表加权求和”；静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `factorized_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`factorized_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。相对 r74 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_topk` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变，直接回答当前高信息量结构问题：在 routed-only sparse-capacity 已连续给出正信号、而 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的容量扩展未继续改善后，把 shared low-rank basis 放进 expert 内部 head，而不是继续只堆 routed-only 容量，是否能在不拉长 active path 的前提下形成新的低到中成本 Pareto 段。若当前瓶颈已从总子库容量转向 scorer 质量与共享结构建模，则这次 matched architecture probe 应在约同一成本带内优于 r74。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 在近同成本下明显优于 r74，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只显式设置 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，确认 shared basis 宽度是否是该结构的主控制旋钮。","如果它接近但不明显优于 r74，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=128`，判断这条结构是否更适合更靠左的低成本段。","如果它明显弱于 r74，则归档当前 `factorized_expert_topk` 原型，后续把低成本结构预算转回 `expert_topk` 容量线或 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 trunk/stage 轴。"],"notes_to_memory":["`factorized_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是静态 expert 子库上的有限加权和，兼容性为扩展兼容。","本轮是对 r74 的严格 matched architecture probe：保持 `K=160 / NUM_EXPERTS=128 / EF=1 / adam / 8e-4` 不变，只切换到 `factorized_expert_topk`，直接测试 expert-internal low-rank / shared-basis expert routing 是否比 routed-only 更值得继续。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 代码路径估算，`factorized_expert_topk K=160 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=128` 的总成本约在 0.49x 附近，仍处于当前要补的低到中成本带内，并显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","r71/r72 的负结果只覆盖较小容量 recipe，不能替代在当前 `NUM_EXPERTS=128` sparse-capacity recipe 下的 fresh matched validation。"],"reference_round":74,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r74 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这比继续在 `expert_topk` 上做第四次纯容量外推或回到旧 family 的 K/LR 邻域更符合当前阶段的结构扩展优先级，因为 routed-only 已给出连续容量正信号，而 r76 说明三段式 family 的低成本瓶颈不主要在继续加 expert 容量；现在更值得回答的是 shared-basis expert routing 是否能在相近成本下提供新的结构收益。主要风险是 `factorized_expert_topk` 的旧原型在较小容量下曾给出负信号，但那不足以否定当前更强 sparse-capacity recipe 下的 matched probe。","summary":"做一轮严格 matched 的 `factorized_expert_topk` 架构探针：以 r74 为参考，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_topk` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，其余 `K=160, NUM_EXPERTS=128, EF=1, adam, lr=8e-4` 全部保持不变。目标不是继续细扫 routed-only 容量线，而是直接判定 `expert-internal low-rank / shared-basis expert routing` 在当前低到中成本带是否值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0133.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e(h(x))}(h(x))} α_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低维投影，e(h(x)) 是轻量 router 选择的单个静态 expert，{b_{e,i}} 是各 expert 的静态子库原子。在线侧可导出为“共享低秩投影 + 单 expert 路由 + expert 内 local top-k + 静态子库查表加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `factorized_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r132 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `two_stage_residual_expert` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答当前高优先级问题“expert 内部 low-rank head / local top-k”是否比 trunk-free staged residual 更值得继续；如果该 family 在约 0.21x total_cost 下明显优于现有 `expert_topk` / `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的低成本负信号，则说明当前低成本带更有价值的不是继续打磨旧 shared+routed 结构，而是把低秩限制放进 expert 内部 head。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.21x 下显著优于现有同级低成本 anchor，则下一轮保持 `factorized_expert_topk` 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128`，继续测试 expert-internal low-rank 是否还能进一步左移。","如果该点只与 `expert_topk` 持平或更差，则可更清楚地判定“expert-specific low-rank head”在当前 target 上也不成立，后续应转向别的未充分验证结构，而不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_*` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert` 上做局部扫参。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `architecture=factorized_expert_topk`、`factorized_hidden_dim=256`、`active_experts=1` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，该 matched recipe 估算 selection≈0.09x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.21x，明显低于 r132 的 0.47x，也低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","这轮相对 r132 是纯架构切换，目标是补上当前 prompt 明确优先的“shared/low-rank basis + expert-specific head / local top-k”结构信息，而不是继续在已连续无改进的 family 上细扫。"],"reference_round":132,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r132 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。当前 `lowrank_expert_topk` 与 `two_stage_residual_expert` 已连续给出非支配失败，继续在这两条线上调内部旋钮的信息增量不高；切到 `factorized_expert_topk` 更符合当前“结构扩展优先”和 prompt 对 expert-internal low-rank 的明确指向。主要风险是该 family 历史上有弱信号，但那是旧轮次弱先验；本轮在当前 target 上用 matched recipe 重验，结论会更干净。","summary":"Round 133 应优先切到新的结构假设，而不是继续打磨最近两条已连续失利的 family。建议以 r132 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk`，在约 0.21x 的更低总成本下直接检验“expert 内部 low-rank head + local top-k”是否能形成新的低成本结构前沿。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0092.json:7:  "family_name": "factorized_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0092.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{e\u2208E(z(x))} \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e(z(x))} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d z(x)=Bx \u662f\u5171\u4eab\u4f4e\u7ef4\u6295\u5f71\uff0cE(z) \u662f\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5c11\u91cf active experts\uff0cexpert \u5185\u7528\u5c0f\u578b low-rank head A_e z \u505a local scoring/top-k\uff0c{B_e} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u201cshared low-rank projection + \u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u9009\u62e9 + \u5b50\u5e93\u5185\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\u201d\u7684 LUTurbo/Lottable \u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `factorized_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8 frontier\u3002\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r86 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `lowrank_expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `factorized_expert_topk`\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 `K=128`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=16`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u548c\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\u65f6\uff0c\u5982\u679c r86 \u7684\u5931\u8d25\u4e3b\u8981\u6765\u81ea full-dim routed scorer \u592a\u91cd\u800c\u4e0d\u662f multi-expert MoE-like \u672c\u8eab\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48 shared-basis expert routing \u5e94\u80fd\u5728\u66f4\u4f4e total_cost \u4e0b\u663e\u8457\u6539\u5584 FVU\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u7ea6 0.3x \u6210\u672c\u5e26\u5f62\u6210\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u6027 anchor\u3002\u6309\u5f53\u524d\u6210\u672c\u6a21\u578b\u7c97\u4f30\uff0cselection\u22480.19x\u3001deployment\u22480.12x\u3001total\u22480.31x\uff0c\u4f4e\u4e8e 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0092.json:20:    "summary": "Round 92 \u7ee7\u7eed\u5b9a\u5411\u8865\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u524d\u6cbf\uff0c\u4f46\u4e0d\u56de\u5230\u65e7 family \u7684 K \u8f74\u5fae\u8c03\u3002\u4ee5 r86 \u4e3a matched reference\uff0c\u53ea\u5207\u6362\u5230 `factorized_expert_topk`\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u201cmulti-expert active path \u7684\u95ee\u9898\u662f\u5728 MoE \u7ed3\u6784\u672c\u8eab\uff0c\u8fd8\u662f\u5728 full-dim scorer \u592a\u91cd\u201d\u8fd9\u4e2a\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u63a2\u7d22\u91cc\u6700\u5173\u952e\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u95ee\u9898\u3002",
